  <brief_title>Combination Chemotherapy With or Without Irinotecan in Treating Patients With Stage III Colon Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Randomized Study of Intensive Adjuvant Chemotherapy for Resected Colon Cancer at High Risk of Recurrence</official_title>
  <sponsors>
